Package: statConsultantAddin
Type: Package
Title: Stat Consultant RStudio Addin
Version: 0.1.0
Description: RStudio Addin for Stat Consultant. Polls the chat backend's
    pending-code queue and inserts received code at the cursor position of
    the active source document (rstudioapi::insertText). Also transparently
    scans the global environment and syncs an aggregate-only, PII-filtered
    snapshot (column names/types/missing counts/category levels — never row
    values) to the backend. Zero-config auth via a local shared-secret file
    the backend generates.
License: Proprietary
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    rstudioapi,
    httr2,
    later
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
